21.title: Falsa muerte
21.plot: Griselda plans a return to Colombia, once again faking death. Not so lucky, Jones is stolen from the hospital and tortured. Jennifer searches D.C for Jones. News of the Black Widow murder reaches Devil.

22.title: Contra el Diablo
22.plot: Griselda makes it back home. Robert is back with Jennifer. El Diablo feels remorseful and contemplates mortality. Antonella is depressed. Dagger forces Robert into sex at gunpoint and plans to rid Jennifer from their lives.

23.title: Respeto Para la Viuda
23.plot: Devil pays respect to the graves. Camel and Guerra plan the Zarco hit. Norm and Angel decide to relocate. Daga leaves to team with Marco and they collaborate with Ferguson. Antonella is a short term runaway. Zarco kills the musicians.

24.title: Mujer Despechada
24.plot: Daga kills the hosts and tracks her prey. Norm falls in pain. The doctors who aided Griselda are assassinated. Devil prepares for Ana. Angel is ambushed getting Norms meds while Daga and Marco storm the cottage.

25.title: Injusta Muerte
25.plot: Daga and Marco seize the cottage and Family. Angel heroically takes down Marco's team. Daga escapes with Ana while Norm kills Marco. Angel suffers a great loss. Griselda learns of Ana's kidnapping. Daga delivers Ana to Devil.

26.title: Llegando a MedellAn
26.plot: The Family are in mourning. Robert is relieved Angel doesn't blame him. Jessica flirts for Intel. Camel has suspicions. Marco and the Mole make a pact unbeknownst to Devil. Daga is Rollin in dinero. The Crew jump into Medellin.

27.title: Muy Cerca del Diablo
27.plot: Norm is hurt from the plane jump but narrowly escapes nearby soldiers. Daga locates the Family and causes some chaos. Griselda and the Crew move in on Zarco at his stable ranch. Mole fits together a piece of the puzzle.

32.title: Plan de Escape
32.plot: Tyler visits Griselda. Tyler gains Godmothers trust and she asks him for a favor. Jones goes with Garcia to offer Griselda a deal. Tyler shadows Sugar. Griselda's new lawyer brings good and bad news. Ritchie coordinates with Juliana.

33.title: Nuevo Amor
33.plot: DEA offers Jones a position back, which he turns down. Griselda and Tyler share an intimate encounter. While discussing Celia reconnaissance job, Ritchi proposes new duties. The DEA is piecing together the next target, JFK Jr.

34.title: Emotivo Reencuentro
34.plot: Michael and Silvio visit Griselda. Michael frustrated nobody will tell him about his Dad runs off. Silvio searches for him. Juliana greenlights Agent Garcia in Medellin Colombia. Katy shoots a vagrant who was trying to hurt Michael.

35.title: El Informante
35.plot: Sugar sees Tyler's an informant, undercover Agent Evans. Katy wants to flee with the boys. Tyler and the DEA put Sugar in the hospital while continuing their operation. Jones writes Griselda telling her she has a betrayer in her midst.
